<plot>Luis, a successful writer in his thirties, travels to Begur (a small town in the Costa Brava) with the intention of finishing his last book. When he asks his ex wife for the keys, he finds out that she has sold the house. Knowing that the new owner is away from Spain on a trip, Jorge moves in to what used to be his house determined to finish his work. However, Elena, the new owner's daughter, decides to spend a few days in Begur. From this point on confusing situations bring the main characters closer and further away from each other.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?367760</url></doc>
